            <h4>1. Introduction</h4>
            <hr />
            <p>
                Welcome to the K9 Koordinator pet care management program. Using this software will allow
                you to perform many routine tasks quickly and easily, making more effective use of your valuable time.
                Its straightforward options make it simple to use and you will be up and running in no time!
            </p>
