                * If you have 1 or 2 employees (small business) you are not classified as a single user or Owner-operated business.
                If you have at least one employee, you need to configure the security setting properly. Configuring security initially,
                allows your security to scale correctly as your business grows.
            </p>
            <p>7.1. <strong>Security Levels</strong> <br /> Go to "Options" -> "Settings" -> "Security" -> "Security levels" <br />
                <br />
                From here you cand "Select" a role to set its security levels, you can add a new role to setup its security levels
