                Once you have used the software for a week or so, and you have a good grasp on what security
                policies you wish to use, then you can safely change the access to 'Administrator / Owner' if you wish.
                <br />
                Default password for "Owner" is "secret"
            </p>
            <br />
            <img ng-src="{{'img_help/help.7.1.png' | baseUrl}}" alt="" />
