            <h4>12. Rewards program setup</h4>
            <hr />
            <p>
                * <strong>Summary</strong>: a ‘Rewards Program’ is a feature similar to ‘Frequent Flier’ programs offered by the air line industry.
                    It allows the business to reward clients for money spend, as well as offer incentives for new client referrals.
                    Every time money is paid, your client will automatically earn ‘Reward Points’ depending on the amount spend.
                    Receipts will include the amount of ‘Reward Points’ earned for the current payment as well as total amount till date. <br />
                <br />
                * Who can skip this step? Businesses that currently do not offer a rewards program.
                    We don’t recommend configuring the rewards program if one is not already in place.
                    Nevertheless, we recommend reading this section if considering the start of a
                    rewards program to assess the overall capabilities of the system. <br />
            </p>
            <p>
                12.1. <strong>Configure</strong>, go to "Options" - "Settings" - "Rewards program" <br />
                1. Make sure the option ‘Rewards Program Active’ is checked. <br />
